      "author_association" : "CONTRIBUTOR",
      "body" : "Ok, how then avoid same situation in future?\nMajority of users are on old (<0.8) versions that use BDB and WILL have same trouble when some mine will create another huge block... \nNew database system is superior to BDB and we should force users at some point to upgrade to avoid same issue in future or limit new versions to not produce blocks that will not be accepted by older clients.\nBut second option will be step back, when BTC become more and more popular there will be more and more txes and blocks will be larger and larger...\n",
